data.eml:eml: Gekko canaensis sp. nov. (Squamata: Gekkonidae), a new gecko from Southern Vietnam

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Tri, Ngo Van, Gamble, Tony (2011): Gekko canaensis sp. nov. (Squamata: Gekkonidae), a new gecko from Southern Vietnam. Zootaxa 2890: 53-64, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.207125
